```
func twoSum(_ nums: [Int], _ target: Int) -> [Int] {
    for i in 0 ..< (nums.count-1) {
        let num1 = nums[i]
        for j in (i+1) ..< nums.count {
            let num2 = nums[j];
            if (num1 + num2 == target) {
                return [i, j];
            }
        }
    }
    return [];
}
```
